easy units if you sign up

00:26:23.300 --> 00:26:25.300 align:middle line:90%
for this weekend workshop.

00:26:25.300 --> 00:26:28.890 align:middle line:84%
So I went running into the
registrar's office, put

00:26:28.890 --> 00:26:29.690 align:middle line:90%
my name.

00:26:29.690 --> 00:26:31.630 align:middle line:84%
I didn't even look at what
the title of the workshop was.

00:26:31.630 --> 00:26:33.044 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah, two easy units.

00:26:33.044 --> 00:26:37.370 align:middle line:84%
>> Two easy units, I put my
name down, and I showed up.

00:26:37.370 --> 00:26:42.050 align:middle line:84%
It was Halloween of
1980 in San Francisco.

00:26:42.050 --> 00:26:45.230 align:middle line:84%
I showed up to this
Friday night session,

00:26:45.230 --> 00:26:48.650 align:middle line:84%
and it was an anthropologist,
who's now deceased,

00:26:48.650 --> 00:26:51.920 align:middle line:84%
Michael Harner,
teaching a course

00:26:51.920 --> 00:26:56.380 align:middle line:84%
