journeying and shamanism.

00:26:56.380 --> 00:27:00.050 align:middle line:84%
And a shaman is a
man or woman who

00:27:00.050 --> 00:27:02.960 align:middle line:84%
goes into an altered
state of consciousness

00:27:02.960 --> 00:27:08.840 align:middle line:84%
and has access to these
amazing helping spirits who

00:27:08.840 --> 00:27:15.120 align:middle line:84%
just want to guide us and heal
us and help us with our life.

00:27:15.120 --> 00:27:19.520 align:middle line:84%
And so I met my helping
spirit, and he just

00:27:19.520 --> 00:27:23.360 align:middle line:84%
started answering all the
questions I had in life,

00:27:23.360 --> 00:27:25.110 align:middle line:90%
and I was hooked.

00:27:25.110 --> 00:27:27.350 align:middle line:90%
I mean, there I was.

00:27:27.350 --> 00:27:31.370 align:middle line:84%
There's this disembodied spirit,
I'm laying down on the floor

00:27:31.370 --> 00:27:35.330 align:middle line:84%
listening to some drumming,
talking to this spirit,

00:27:35.330 --> 00:27:39.290 align:middle line:84%
telling me all the questions,
unanswered questions

00:27:39.290 --> 00:27:42.710 align:middle line:84%
I have in my life
and what I need to do

00:27:42.710 --> 00:27:44.970 align:middle line:90%
and why I'm having issues.

00:27:44.970 --> 00:27:48.860 align:middle line:84%
And I was like, this
is what I was looking

00:27:48.860 --> 00:27:53.235 align:middle line:84%
for because I'd been looking
for spiritual practices because

00:27:53.235 --> 00:27:54.035 align:middle line:90%
of my--

00:27:54.035 --> 00:27:54.835 align:middle line:90%
>> Obviously.

00:27:54.835 --> 00:27:56.660 align:middle line:90%
>> Opening experiences.

00:27:56.660 --> 00:28:02.940 align:middle line:84%
But I couldn't find a path,
and shamanism gave me a path.

00:28:02.940 --> 00:28:09.560 align:middle line:84%
And so then, since 1980,
I've devoted every single day

00:28:09.560 --> 00:28:15.320 align:middle line:84%
to that path, which has taken
me through twists and turns

00:28:15.320 --> 00:28:18.290 align:middle line:84%
and started with
shamanic journeying,

00:28:18.290 --> 00:28:24.410 align:middle line:84%
but moved to teaching about
working with reversing

00:28:24.410 --> 00:28:28.250 align:middle line:84%
environmental pollution,
to moving to teaching

00:28:28.250 --> 00:28:30.430 align:middle line:90%
how to perform ceremonies.

00:28:30.430 --> 00:28:33.710 align:middle line:84%
And I became best
known for my work

00:28:33.710 --> 00:28:38.310 align:middle line:84%
with helping people bring
back the parts of their soul.

00:28:38.310 --> 00:28:39.352 align:middle line:90%
>> Soul retrieval.

00:28:39.352 --> 00:28:40.310 align:middle line:90%
>> Their vital essence.

00:28:40.310 --> 00:28:42.400 align:middle line:84%
>> I wanted to spend some time
talking about that actually.

00:28:42.400 --> 00:28:43.200 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:28:43.200 --> 00:28:47.270 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, so it's been
over 30 years of--

00:28:47.270 --> 00:28:48.720 align:middle line:90%
>> Coming up on 40 years.

00:28:48.720 --> 00:28:50.660 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah, it's coming up on 40.

00:28:50.660 --> 00:28:53.120 align:middle line:84%
There's always another
door to walk through.

00:28:53.120 --> 00:28:58.730 align:middle line:84%
I haven't even begun to learn
about the power of this work.

00:28:58.730 --> 00:29:00.190 align:middle line:90%
It's really amazing.

00:29:00.190 --> 00:29:03.140 align:middle line:84%
>> And what's flowing into my
mind right now is I'm thinking

00:29:03.140 --> 00:29:06.110 align:middle line:84%
that this was your path in a
