00:30:52.920 --> 00:30:55.170 align:middle line:90%
and one who knows.

00:30:55.170 --> 00:30:59.880 align:middle line:84%
And so there are so many
initiations to the path

00:30:59.880 --> 00:31:07.470 align:middle line:84%
