00:31:31.490 --> 00:31:37.650 align:middle line:84%
>> Yeah, the dimensions
of reality, the spirits,

00:31:37.650 --> 00:31:42.150 align:middle line:84%
the plants, the
crystals, the trees,

00:31:42.150 --> 00:31:48.180 align:middle line:84%
