00:32:08.550 --> 00:32:10.860 align:middle line:90%
I mean, it's magnificent.

00:32:10.860 --> 00:32:15.390 align:middle line:84%
But people from all over the
world, all walks of life,

00:32:15.390 --> 00:32:18.570 align:middle line:84%
can be a shaman
when they've gone

00:32:18.570 --> 00:32:22.710 align:middle line:84%
through the initiation that
brings them to one who knows.

00:32:22.710 --> 00:32:23.610 align:middle line:90%
>> And it just--

00:32:23.610 --> 00:32:30.810 align:middle line:84%
it's heartbreaking to think
of how our minds have been

00:32:30.810 --> 00:32:34.620 align:middle line:84%
funneled down such a narrow
chute of understanding

00:32:34.620 --> 00:32:37.015 align:middle line:84%
and even the
perception of reality.

00:32:37.015 --> 00:32:40.830 align:middle line:90%


00:32:40.830 --> 00:32:44.250 align:middle line:84%
Most people live in
such a dry understanding

00:32:44.250 --> 00:32:48.690 align:middle line:84%
