in its multi-dimensional full

00:32:54.030 --> 00:32:55.830 align:middle line:90%
living color form.

00:32:55.830 --> 00:32:59.468 align:middle line:84%
All things have those dimensions
to it, not just humans.

00:32:59.468 --> 00:33:01.260 align:middle line:84%
