we're multidimensional.

00:33:01.260 --> 00:33:02.140 align:middle line:90%
So is every planet.

00:33:02.140 --> 00:33:03.930 align:middle line:90%
So is the earth herself.

00:33:03.930 --> 00:33:06.180 align:middle line:84%
And being able to travel
into those higher realms,

00:33:06.180 --> 00:33:09.570 align:middle line:84%
and to me, that's, I think,
maybe the most beautiful thing

00:33:09.570 --> 00:33:12.600 align:middle line:84%
about shamanic work
that people like you do

00:33:12.600 --> 00:33:15.300 align:middle line:84%
and people who guide
others into this

00:33:15.300 --> 00:33:19.210 align:middle line:84%
is to open up the realm
of beauty and possibility.

00:33:19.210 --> 00:33:25.710 align:middle line:84%
>> And so what happens is
