00:33:29.430 --> 00:33:33.330 align:middle line:84%
They open up to the beauty
of their inner landscape,

00:33:33.330 --> 00:33:37.140 align:middle line:84%
because what's happening
now in the world

00:33:37.140 --> 00:33:40.590 align:middle line:84%
we live in is life has
become meaningless.

00:33:40.590 --> 00:33:42.450 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes, truly.

00:33:42.450 --> 00:33:46.410 align:middle line:84%
